🏅🎉AOV in Asian Games 2018 as Demonstration Sport!🎉🏅

Dear Challengers! For the first time, eSports will be featured at the Asian Games 2018 as a Demonstration Sport!

First held in 1951, the Asian Games is the largest and most iconic sporting event in Asia recognized by the International Olympic Committee (IOC).

...

Today, the AESF (http://bit.ly/AoVatAsianGames2018) has announced that AOV has been chosen to be featured as a Demonstration Sports at the Asian Games!!!

This also means that in the future, we will have a chance to be a medal sport.

We are very happy that eSports is receiving more and more attention at the regional stage! Let's keep an eye on this together!

☀ Free Vouchers!
1.) X number of Vouchers based on the number of attendees. (Example: If there's 37 attendees, everyone will get 37 vouchers each!)

-Win More vouchers
